                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> III <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iun</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan> di<supplied reason="lost">e Iovis Tibe</supplied><lb break="no" n="1"/>riano II et D<supplied reason="lost">ione <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei aneinanderpassende Fragmente, Neulesung durch neu angepasstes Fragment (b) bei Piso. Zeile 2: ET-Ligatur. (B): AE 1982; Jobst: &amp;quot;&amp;quot;III Id(us) Iun(ias) Di[ocle]/[tia?]no II et [--- co(n)s(ulibus); Vorbeck: III id(us) Iun(ias) Di[---] / [---]no II et [--- co(n)s(ulibus)].</p>
            </div>
